node.text: Selamat Hari Raya to you and your beautiful family ❤️❤️❤️

Today was a Zoom-(cov)Eid celebration.
It was also a binge-eating kind of day.
Thank you to our family and friends for all the delicious dishes and desserts that were sent over the last few days.

Our hearts are warm, our bellies are full.
And we all had a real good time.

Selamat Hari Raya!
